headline: WeRide, Uber To Deploy 1,200 Robotaxis In The Middle East
summary: WeRide Inc. and Uber Technologies, Inc. (NYSE:UBER) announced a major expansion of their strategic partnership to deploy at least 1,200 Robotaxis across the Middle East, marking one of the largest commercial autonomous mobility rollouts in the region. The deployment will span Abu Dhabi, Dubai, and Riyadh, with completion targeted as soon as 2027.
